For Signed APK (Release):

  # Using your existing keystore and build.json
  cordova build android --release --buildConfig=build.json -- --packageType=apk

  Output: app/build/outputs/apk/release/app-release.apk

  For Unsigned APK (Debug/Testing):

  # Debug APK (unsigned, for testing only)
  cordova build android

  Output: app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk

  Alternative commands:

  # Clean and rebuild
  cordova clean android
  cordova build android --release --buildConfig=build.json -- --packageType=apk

  # For AAB (Google Play Store)
  cordova build android --release --buildConfig=build.json -- --packageType=bundle

